1021
01:31:16,829 --> 01:31:19,627
I needed her so much as a child.

1022
01:31:34,309 --> 01:31:37,585
I hope you don't mind,
I had your desk brought in.

1023
01:31:40,869 --> 01:31:44,703
- Don't I have a say in this?
- No! (laughs)

1024
